content: I think that's a great starting point. I'd like to dedicate 5-6 days a week to fitness, with one or two rest days. My availability is pretty flexible, but I prefer morning workouts. As for goals, I'd like to focus on improving my overall endurance and balance, with a slight emphasis on soccer performance since we're in the middle of the league season. By the way, speaking of soccer, it's crazy how much I've improved since joining the league 3 months ago - I hadn't played in 2 years prior, and it's amazing how quickly my skills have come back.
